Hello guys, I`ve seen many 317`s without the ::item command. They mostly had the ::pickup, or ::spawn command.
This is way better, it`s spawning system like for 508`s.

Here.
[code] if (command.startsWith("item") && (playerRights >= 2)) {
                String[] args = command.split(" ");
                if (args.length == 3) {
                    int chi = Integer.parseInt(args[1]);
                    int kitory = Integer.parseInt(args[2]);
                    for(int i = chi; i <= kitory; i++) {
                        addItem(i, 1);
                    }
                }
            }[/code]
At the moment it`s only Administrator+ free spawn.
If you wanna make free spawn for all players change the :
<blockquote>&& (playerRights >= 2)) {</blockquote>
to
<blockquote>&& (playerRights >= 0)) {</blockquote>
If you wish it to be mod+, change it to :
<blockquote>&& (playerRights >= 1)) {</blockquote>
If you wish it to be Owner/co owner + change it to :
<blockquote>&& (playerRights >= 3)) {</blockquote>

Reply if you got any problem.

